\[\Gamma^2_{22} = 0\]

\[\Gamma^2_{23} = \frac{1}{2} g^{22} g_{22, 3} = - \frac{1}{2} E_{+, 3}\]

\[\Gamma^3_{00} = \Gamma^3_{10} = \Gamma^3_{20} 
